{"tid":2397252,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"發覺呢兩種人應該係同一班人黎...","createTime":"2021-02-06T09:21:18.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-07T14:22:56.000Z","uid":37146,"like":13,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"4fe8eb0ef3a9c18d0219364c915fe6cfd562944c","tid":2397252,"uid":37146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T09:21:18.000Z","msg":"呢兩種人買股票共通點係<br />\n諗野講野偏幼稚<br />\n意見不同就開屌<br />\n買賣股票帶感情<br />\n乜鳩都關政治事<br />\n就係GME賤種同反中資股賤種<br />\n<br />\nGME賤種：<br />\n為公義！唔買GME就係社工打手淡友，買就係手足！<br />\n為公義！買GME賺錢與否唔重要，我地係為左打爆沽空機構！<br />\n唔SH死全家！止賺死全家！止蝕死全家！<br />\n（最後大部份輸到仆街，嗌生嗌死，跳撚晒樓）<br />\n<br />\n反中資股賤種：<br />\n為反共！買中資股就係藍絲，唔買就係黃絲！<br />\n為反共！買中資股可以賺錢又點？我地買股唔係為賺錢！<br />\n買中資股就係支那狗，支那狗全家死清光！<br />\n（最後都係會買港股，美股又照買阿木ETF，明明阿木ETF有中資股成分）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"violet\"><strong>結論：呢兩種人都係賤種黎<br />\n<br />\n好大機會係同一班人黎...</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"6999b60a01792520acb7afb6d3caf94f0190600b","tid":2397252,"uid":99885,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T09:24:14.000Z","msg":"樓主都係賤種黎"},{"pid":"78466d3ee06e88dc3de498d6334e89ea34c46430","tid":2397252,"uid":37146,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"6999b60a01792520acb7afb6d3caf94f0190600b","tid":2397252,"uid":99885,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T09:24:14.000Z","msg":"樓主都係賤種黎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T09:24:57.000Z","msg":"咪撚盲反=,="},{"pid":"1c5d1c9f3ceb0483e2e154fdef730ff80da164ad","tid":2397252,"uid":34929,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T09:30:48.000Z","msg":"咪又係cctoy 班弱智<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8535eca340140890f66744a4957eae03fade2fb","tid":2397252,"uid":375585,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T09:31:59.000Z","msg":"GME買咗幾股食花生only<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> btw樓主係咁隔幾日又開post狙擊唔悶咩"},{"pid":"a83e690829c6c79dd9d1c11a2fa194a089